title: 3 Storybooks for Children (gnv64)
description:
I have scanned three illustrated storybooks for children, all published by Manoj Publications. All are in PDF format with OCR, bookmarks & covers. Don't forget to seed after you download for others to enjoy!

1. Ghost Stories Collected by Ganga Prasad Sharma
ISBN: 978-81-8133-485-5 | 2012 | 170 pages | 5.85 mb

2. Real Life Encounters with Ghosts & Spirits by P.V.Rao
ISBN: 978-81-310-0623-8 | 2012 | 143 pages | 5.34 mb

3. World Famous Bravery Tales Compiled By Ganga Prasad Sharma
ISBN: 978-81-310-0099-1 | 2013 | 158 pages | 6.79 mb
